### NduthiRide — Tracking (WebSocket reference)
### The Tracking feature is WebSocket-only — no REST endpoints.
### Use this file as a reference for the events and payloads.
###
### ─── Connection ───────────────────────────────────────────────
### URL:  ws://localhost:3000/tracking
### Auth: socket.handshake.auth = { token: "<accessToken>" }
###
### After connection the server automatically:
###   - Joins the socket to room "account:<accountId>"
###   - For riders: also joins "riders" room
###
### ─── Client → Server events ───────────────────────────────────
###
###   rider:location-update
###   Payload: { lat: number, lng: number, speed?: number }
###   Description: Rider sends their GPS position; server persists to
###                LocationHistory, updates Rider.currentLat/Lng, and
###                pushes to the active ride's user room.
###
###   rider:toggle-availability
###   Payload: { isAvailable: boolean }
###   Description: Rider goes online or offline.
###
### ─── Server → Client events ───────────────────────────────────
###
###   tracking:location
###   Payload: { riderId, lat, lng, speed?, timestamp }
###   Sent to: room "account:<userId>" of the active ride's user
###
###   ride:new-request
###   Payload: { rideId, pickupAddress, dropoffAddress, estimatedFare, distanceKm, user: { ... } }
###   Sent to: room "riders" when a new ride is PENDING
###
###   parcel:new-request
###   Payload: { parcelId, pickupAddress, dropoffAddress, deliveryFee, distanceKm, user: { ... } }
###   Sent to: room "riders" when a new parcel delivery is PENDING
###
###   ride:accepted / parcel:accepted
###   Payload: { rideId/parcelId, rider: { id, fullName, phone, bikeRegistration, bikeModel, ratingAverage } }
###   Sent to: room "account:<userId>" when a rider accepts

### ─── REST: Get nearby available riders ───────────────────────
### (This one is REST, not WebSocket)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1
@userToken = <paste_user_access_token_here>

GET {{baseUrl}}/riders/nearby?lat=-1.2921&lng=36.8219&radiusKm=5
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
